1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,962
=Episode 28=

3
00:00:16,800 --> 00:00:17,399
Take this.

4
00:00:26,600 --> 00:00:28,359
Do you really want me dead that badly?

5
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:35,000
Yu, what are you waiting for?

6
00:00:35,920 --> 00:00:38,159
You can't let your father's murder
go unavenged!

7
00:00:38,799 --> 00:00:39,520
Yu!

8
00:00:41,359 --> 00:00:42,000
Yu!

9
00:00:47,880 --> 00:00:49,079
If you can't do it, I will!

10
00:00:51,159 --> 00:00:52,799
You bold little thief!

11
00:00:53,240 --> 00:00:54,799
How dare you break into the Gate Bureau!

12
00:00:55,159 --> 00:00:56,600
I'll catch you alive!

13
00:00:57,799 --> 00:00:58,880
Get up!

14
00:01:01,640 --> 00:01:02,520
I...

15
00:01:03,079 --> 00:01:04,159
Mercy, please! Spare me!

16
00:01:04,159 --> 00:01:04,799
Wushuang!

17
00:01:05,560 --> 00:01:06,400
Help me!

18
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:08,400
Chu Yunchang!

19
00:01:08,760 --> 00:01:09,799
Let him go!

20
00:01:10,040 --> 00:01:10,920
Or I'll make you pay!

21
00:01:10,920 --> 00:01:11,519
Hold on!

22
00:01:11,599 --> 00:01:12,640
Watch where you're aiming!

23
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:14,159
I'm the only son in this family!

24
00:01:14,159 --> 00:01:16,560
This vile lady kills without remorse!

25
00:01:31,319 --> 00:01:32,040
Let's go!

26
00:01:32,519 --> 00:01:33,079
Wushuang!

27
00:01:33,239 --> 00:01:34,719
She's taking me with her!

28
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:36,400
- Help me!
- Chu Yunchang!

29
00:01:36,400 --> 00:01:37,319
Let him go!

30
00:01:41,319 --> 00:01:41,959
Chu Yunchang!

31
00:01:43,760 --> 00:01:44,480
It's all my fault.

32
00:01:47,480 --> 00:01:48,439
It's all my fault.

33
00:01:50,319 --> 00:01:51,000
Father...

34
00:01:53,359 --> 00:01:54,159
Father!

35
00:01:55,159 --> 00:01:56,319
Sister, are you okay?

36
00:02:00,580 --> 00:02:01,480
This is all your fault!

37
00:02:01,719 --> 00:02:03,799
Not a single person
in the Gate Bureau is any good!

38
00:02:03,799 --> 00:02:04,400
I...

39
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:05,159
I should kill you!

40
00:02:05,519 --> 00:02:06,200
Zhizhi!

41
00:02:08,039 --> 00:02:09,400
He saved me back there.

42
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:10,240
But...

43
00:02:11,319 --> 00:02:11,919
Sister!

44
00:02:13,479 --> 00:02:15,120
Sister, what's wrong?

45
00:02:16,039 --> 00:02:18,280
My father...

46
00:02:21,039 --> 00:02:22,759
The shock must have been
too much for her.

47
00:02:22,759 --> 00:02:23,790
It's overwhelmed her heart.

48
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:25,520
We'd better get out of here.

49
00:02:25,520 --> 00:02:26,080
Right.

50
00:02:26,090 --> 00:02:27,080
I'll carry her. Come on.

51
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:27,840
Quick!

52
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:32,639
Let's go.

53
00:02:36,550 --> 00:02:38,587
(Big Buddha Temple)

54
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:47,400
Brother!

55
00:02:49,479 --> 00:02:51,719
What a tragic death...

56
00:02:59,199 --> 00:02:59,840
Is it true

57
00:03:03,000 --> 00:03:04,120
Chief Mao is dead, too?

58
00:03:05,599 --> 00:03:06,759
I saw it with my own eyes.

59
00:03:07,360 --> 00:03:08,199
From the look of it,

60
00:03:08,759 --> 00:03:09,759
he and Yunchang's father

61
00:03:10,759 --> 00:03:12,960
killed each other.

62
00:03:13,439 --> 00:03:15,680
Mao Buyu is the worst!

63
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:17,560
He's blaming everything

64
00:03:17,719 --> 00:03:19,120
on Yunchang.

65
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:20,400
He even tried to cut her down.

66
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:22,120
This is outrageous!

67
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:23,800
Where are you going?

68
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:26,360
Settling the score with Mao Buyu.

69
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:27,520
I'm coming with you.

70
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:28,439
Hold it.

71
00:03:31,639 --> 00:03:32,240
Yunchang...

72
00:03:34,599 --> 00:03:36,000
Nobody move.

73
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:37,159
Chang.

74
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:38,400
What do you mean by this?

75
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:41,159
My father

76
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:44,439
was killed because he was searching

77
00:03:44,719 --> 00:03:45,680
for the Sacred Token.

78
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:48,159
What we should be doing right now

79
00:03:48,800 --> 00:03:50,240
isn't seeking revenge.

80
00:03:52,700 --> 00:03:54,360
We need to fulfill
my father's final wish.

81
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:57,000
So, what's our next move?

82
00:04:02,199 --> 00:04:03,080
Carry on.

83
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:04,600
I'll see if there are any pursuers.

84
00:04:08,479 --> 00:04:09,360
We go to Xichuan.

85
00:04:10,719 --> 00:04:13,000
As Sect Leader
of the Sacred Hand Sect,

86
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:14,360
I order all of you

87
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:16,040
to find Dongfang Bai,

88
00:04:16,439 --> 00:04:18,199
and uncover the truth
about the Sacred Token

89
00:04:19,600 --> 00:04:21,690
Fulfill the dying wishes
of my father and grandfather.

90
00:04:23,060 --> 00:04:25,100
- Your wish is our command.
- Your wish is our command.

91
00:04:42,837 --> 00:04:47,112
(Memorial, The Late Father Mao Jixian)

92
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,040
Father!

93
00:05:17,360 --> 00:05:17,959
Father...

94
00:05:24,839 --> 00:05:25,680
It's all your fault.

95
00:05:26,199 --> 00:05:27,759
You brought the enemy into our home!

96
00:05:30,480 --> 00:05:32,199
Say something, Mao Buyu!

97
00:05:33,519 --> 00:05:34,399
Say something!

98
00:05:34,399 --> 00:05:35,040
Even now,

99
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,920
are you still trying
to protect Chu Yunchang?

100
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:38,560
Why are you still protecting her?

101
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:40,240
Say something, Mao Buyu!

102
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,560
- Start talking!
- My dear.

103
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:43,680
How can you blame Buyu for this?

104
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:45,079
Who else is there to blame?

105
00:05:46,319 --> 00:05:47,360
If it weren't for you,

106
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:49,000
our father would still be alive.

107
00:05:50,439 --> 00:05:51,920
Say something, Mao Buyu!

108
00:05:52,639 --> 00:05:53,600
Start talking!

109
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:55,759
Talk to me!

110
00:05:55,959 --> 00:05:57,360
My dear.

111
00:05:57,759 --> 00:05:59,199
Please.

112
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,639
I'll never forgive you!

113
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:07,279
Let's go.

114
00:06:20,959 --> 00:06:21,519
Come here.

115
00:06:23,262 --> 00:06:24,600
Why are you pulling me?

116
00:06:26,519 --> 00:06:27,160
My dear.

117
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:30,360
My dear.

118
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:31,720
I know you're hurting.

119
00:06:32,079 --> 00:06:33,120
But this tragedy

120
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:35,120
had nothing to do with Yunchang.

121
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:37,399
What did you say?

122
00:06:37,959 --> 00:06:38,839
Look, if we're saying

123
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:40,800
Yunchang's father killed your father,

124
00:06:41,160 --> 00:06:42,160
then her father

125
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:43,720
was killed by him, too.

126
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:44,800
Anran!

127
00:06:45,200 --> 00:06:46,920
I can't believe
you're defending our enemy!

128
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:48,600
I'm not defending an enemy.

129
00:06:48,879 --> 00:06:50,439
My dear, you're a constable.

130
00:06:50,439 --> 00:06:52,519
You need to keep a level head.

131
00:06:53,279 --> 00:06:54,360
Xu Anran!

132
00:06:57,800 --> 00:06:58,519
Constable Mao.

133
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,279
By the Commissioner's orders,

134
00:07:00,279 --> 00:07:02,160
you're clear
to take the body home for burial.

135
00:07:02,279 --> 00:07:04,279
What's the official explanation
for what happened?

136
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:06,079
Thieves broke into the Gate Bureau.

137
00:07:06,079 --> 00:07:07,600
Chief Mao died in the line of duty.

138
00:07:07,759 --> 00:07:10,279
The Personnel Corps has
already recorded his merit

139
00:07:10,279 --> 00:07:11,500
with the Ministry of Justice.

140
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:13,279
What?

141
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:17,920
This is all so haphazard.

142
00:07:20,759 --> 00:07:24,399
Chu Xiangshan died
in the Commissioner's study?

143
00:07:24,879 --> 00:07:25,480
Yes.

144
00:07:25,759 --> 00:07:27,040
And dying alongside him

145
00:07:27,120 --> 00:07:28,680
was Mao Jixian from the Probe Corps.

146
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:30,680
The sheer audacity of it!

147
00:07:36,079 --> 00:07:38,560
Go. Bring Mao Buyu to me.

148
00:07:39,279 --> 00:07:39,839
Understood.

149
00:07:42,137 --> 00:07:45,087
(In Memorial)

150
00:07:47,650 --> 00:07:49,912
(In Memorial)

151
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:11,879
Buyu, the dead aren't coming back.

152
00:08:12,639 --> 00:08:13,639
We who are still here

153
00:08:14,680 --> 00:08:15,839
must find a way

154
00:08:15,839 --> 00:08:17,680
to avenge the fallen.

155
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:21,759
Yu.

156
00:08:24,879 --> 00:08:25,959
Pull yourself together.

157
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:29,639
Avenge them.

158
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,240
Find the real killer.

159
00:08:36,279 --> 00:08:37,399
Exact vengeance.

160
00:08:41,190 --> 00:08:42,799
The killer has already been dealt with.

161
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:46,759
But we can't let Yunchang
get away with this.

162
00:08:48,879 --> 00:08:49,480
Yu.

163
00:08:50,639 --> 00:08:52,159
My men are gathering information.

164
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:53,600
As soon as we have a lead,

165
00:08:55,679 --> 00:08:57,200
I'll personally lead the arrest.

166
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:59,720
I'll capture Yunchang's entire family.

167
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:03,080
We will put Uncle Mao's soul to rest.

168
00:09:49,437 --> 00:09:52,662
(Ministry of Justice)

169
00:09:52,662 --> 00:09:54,950
(In Memorial)

170
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,559
(In Memorial: Master Mao Jixian)
My dear, wait a moment.

171
00:09:56,559 --> 00:10:00,840
(In Memorial: Master Mao Jixian)
(Ministry of Justice)

172
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:01,480
My dear.

173
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:05,159
Something feels off about all this.

174
00:10:05,759 --> 00:10:06,759
What's off about it?

175
00:10:07,279 --> 00:10:09,159
As the Coroner,
I should perform an autopsy.

176
00:10:09,559 --> 00:10:10,639
But the Commissioner

177
00:10:10,919 --> 00:10:13,200
ordered the body home
for burial immediately.

178
00:10:13,519 --> 00:10:14,519
That seems wrong.

179
00:10:15,860 --> 00:10:16,879
You want to do an autopsy?

180
00:10:17,799 --> 00:10:20,240
I need to establish
the exact time and cause of death.

181
00:10:20,380 --> 00:10:21,679
What's there left to establish?

182
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:22,519
My father

183
00:10:22,519 --> 00:10:24,320
was murdered by Chu Yunchang's father.

184
00:10:24,320 --> 00:10:25,399
But...

185
00:10:25,662 --> 00:10:26,583
No more excuses!

186
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:27,799
Xu Anran,

187
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:29,720
if you dare touch my father's coffin,

188
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:31,000
I'll divorce you.

189
00:10:33,559 --> 00:10:34,240
Lift the coffin!

190
00:10:34,625 --> 00:10:39,937
(Ministry of Justice)

191
00:10:40,037 --> 00:10:42,412
(Coroner's Office)

192
00:10:50,879 --> 00:10:52,320
What are you...

193
00:10:56,090 --> 00:10:57,120
Do you have a death wish?

194
00:10:59,480 --> 00:11:00,879
You've got some nerve.

195
00:11:00,879 --> 00:11:03,240
Stealing a body
from the Gate Bureau in broad daylight?

196
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:06,720
He needs a proper burial.

197
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:07,840
I need to perform an autopsy.

198
00:11:08,120 --> 00:11:09,300
What is there left to examine?

199
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:11,879
Don't you want to know the truth?

200
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:17,600
Examine your father-in-law instead.

201
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:18,559
I'm in a hurry.

202
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:24,360
But my wife

203
00:11:25,679 --> 00:11:26,679
won't let me do it.

204
00:11:27,125 --> 00:11:28,325
And I certainly won't let you.

205
00:11:29,320 --> 00:11:30,240
Figure it out yourself.

206
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:37,399
What's with all of you?

207
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:39,559
Why is everyone so impulsive?

208
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:43,937
(Memorial Tablet
of the late Father Mao Jixian)

209
00:11:45,879 --> 00:11:46,720
Father-in-law,

210
00:11:47,240 --> 00:11:49,720
please forgive my intrusion.

211
00:12:23,399 --> 00:12:24,679
Anran, what are you doing?

212
00:12:26,799 --> 00:12:27,440
Buyu.

213
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:29,480
I have something to tell you.

214
00:12:31,960 --> 00:12:34,200
There's something suspicious
about your father's death.

215
00:12:36,787 --> 00:12:38,840
(In Memorial)

216
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:39,519
Yu.

217
00:12:39,879 --> 00:12:41,559
(Gate Bureau Classified)
I've found a lead.

218
00:12:43,337 --> 00:12:46,687
(Gate Bureau Classified)

219
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:54,399
Since Chu Yunchang fled
from the Big Buddha Temple,

220
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:57,399
the Intel Corps has been
searching everywhere for intel.

221
00:12:58,000 --> 00:13:00,720
Word is there's been unusual activity
in the Ghost Market lately,

222
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:02,960
that the King of Thieves has
forged a new identity.

223
00:13:02,960 --> 00:13:04,879
It seems they're planning
go into hiding.

224
00:13:05,399 --> 00:13:06,320
I believe

225
00:13:06,559 --> 00:13:09,000
the Yunchang family has
only two possible escape routes.

226
00:13:09,759 --> 00:13:11,399
Constable Luo, look here.

227
00:13:11,759 --> 00:13:13,519
(Jiangxi, Jiangnan)
They'll can head south toward Jiangnan,

228
00:13:13,799 --> 00:13:15,279
(Central Shu)
or flee toward Central Shu.

229
00:13:15,679 --> 00:13:17,039
Based on my experience,

230
00:13:17,279 --> 00:13:19,200
it's much more likely that
they're heading for Shu.

231
00:13:22,425 --> 00:13:32,612
(Tomb of the late Father Chu,
remembered by his daughter Yunchang)

232
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:57,440
Chang.

233
00:13:58,720 --> 00:13:59,360
My dear.

234
00:14:00,720 --> 00:14:01,639
It's time to go.

235
00:14:03,559 --> 00:14:04,159
Father.

236
00:14:04,679 --> 00:14:05,919
We're really leaving now.

237
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:09,399
I hope your spirit

238
00:14:09,480 --> 00:14:11,120
will grant us a safe journey to Shu.

239
00:14:11,919 --> 00:14:13,080
To find Dongfang Bai

240
00:14:13,600 --> 00:14:15,159
and uncover the truth.

241
00:14:17,325 --> 00:14:20,525
(Tomb of the late Father Chu,
remembered by his daughter Yunchang)

242
00:14:33,279 --> 00:14:35,559
(You can't let your father's murder
go unavenged!)

243
00:14:35,799 --> 00:14:36,559
(Yu!)

244
00:14:37,519 --> 00:14:38,919
(Are you going
to ignore Uncle Mao's death)

245
00:14:39,639 --> 00:14:41,399
(just because of this woman?)

246
00:14:44,759 --> 00:14:45,399
Take it.

247
00:14:48,425 --> 00:14:52,212
♪Playing a part with a hollow smile♪

248
00:14:53,039 --> 00:14:53,799
(I love you)

249
00:14:54,320 --> 00:14:55,639
(because you're Mao Buyu.)

250
00:14:56,159 --> 00:14:58,080
(It has nothing to do with your status.)

251
00:15:00,159 --> 00:15:01,039
(I lied to you)

252
00:15:02,080 --> 00:15:03,799
(because I didn't want to lose you.)

253
00:15:04,675 --> 00:15:07,862
♪This fervor is buried deep within♪

254
00:15:08,879 --> 00:15:09,919
(What if...)

255
00:15:10,240 --> 00:15:11,799
(I really were the Jade Squirrel,)

256
00:15:12,480 --> 00:15:14,399
(would you still marry me?)

257
00:15:14,879 --> 00:15:15,600
(I would.)

258
00:15:16,020 --> 00:15:17,810
No matter how many years
you're sentenced to,

259
00:15:18,120 --> 00:15:19,120
I'll wait for you.

260
00:15:22,080 --> 00:15:24,120
(I haven't harmed
a soul in my entire life.)

261
00:15:25,080 --> 00:15:26,480
(My only mistake)

262
00:15:28,360 --> 00:15:29,600
(was falling in love with you.)

263
00:15:29,637 --> 00:15:40,525
♪Let's return to when we first met♪

264
00:15:46,525 --> 00:15:49,800
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

265
00:15:49,838 --> 00:15:52,713
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

266
00:15:53,213 --> 00:15:58,931
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

267
00:16:00,113 --> 00:16:03,433
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

268
00:16:03,563 --> 00:16:06,483
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

269
00:16:07,651 --> 00:16:12,891
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

270
00:16:14,113 --> 00:16:16,506
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

271
00:16:16,506 --> 00:16:20,156
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

272
00:16:20,225 --> 00:16:23,715
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

273
00:16:23,813 --> 00:16:26,788
♪To the ends of time♪

274
00:16:26,788 --> 00:16:30,163
♪The moon traces your face♪

275
00:16:30,350 --> 00:16:33,938
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

276
00:16:33,938 --> 00:16:40,178
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

277
00:16:40,513 --> 00:16:43,728
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

278
00:16:44,013 --> 00:16:47,551
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

279
00:16:47,838 --> 00:16:50,863
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

280
00:16:50,863 --> 00:16:53,963
